{"type":"message","id":"c4c15cb9","parentId":"04e3cf7c","timestamp":"2026-03-17T15:46:52.467Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"在 macOS 上启动 Ollama 模型通常是这几步：\n\n1. **确认 Ollama 已经安装**：如果没装，先去 https://ollama.com 下载安装\n2. **启动 Ollama 服务**：安装后打开 Ollama 应用，它会自动在后台运行服务，也可以命令行启动：\n   ```bash\n   ollama serve\n   ```\n3. **拉取你要的模型**：你已经有 `qwen3.5:4b` 了，这步可以跳过，如果没有就运行：\n   ```bash\n   ollama pull qwen3.5:4b\n   ```\n4. **运行测试**：直接运行对话测试模型：\n   ```bash\n   ollama run qwen3.5:4b\n   ```\n\nOllama 默认会监听 `http://localhost:11434`，OpenClaw 如果要连接本地 Ollama，需要在配置里添加 Ollama 模型源，你需要我帮你检查配置吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773762407343}}
